title: "Cheating" may have affected EU referendum result - Wylie
text:
"Cheating" may have affected EU referendum result - Wylie Tuesday, March 27, 2018 - 01:50 
Cambridge Analytica whistleblower Christopher Wylie has told a UK parliamentary committee that he believes it ''reasonable'' to think the outcome of the Brexit vote was could have been altered by cheating. David Pollard reports.
